    "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:1:61",
    "titles": {
      "en": "Do not fight the Kharijites after me!"
    },
    "verse_count": 3,
    "verse_start_index": 234,
    "verse_translations": [
      "en.sayed-ali-raza"
    ],
    "verses": [
      {
        "index": 235,
        "local_index": 1,
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:1:61:1",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/1/61/1",
        "text": [
          "وقال عليه السلام في الخوارج"
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "Amīr al-mu’minīn also said concerning the Khārijites:"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 236,
        "local_index": 2,
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:1:61:2",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/1/61/2",
        "text": [
          "لاَ تَقْتُلُوا الْخَوَارِجَ بَعْدِي، فَلَيْسَ مَنْ طَلَبَ الْحَقَّ فَأَخْطَأَهُ، كَمَنْ طَلَبَ الْبَاطِلَ فَأَدْرَكَهُ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "Do not fight [1] the Khārijites after me, because one who seeks right but does not find it, is not like one who seeks wrong and finds it."
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 237,
        "local_index": 3,
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:1:61:3",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/1/61/3",
        "text": [
          "قال السيد الشريف: يعني معاوية وأصحابه."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "as-Sayyid ar-Raḍī says: Amīr al-mu’minīn means Mu‘āwiyah and his men."
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "index": "nahj-al-balagha:1:61",
